These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Flower: balloon-flower, daffodil, begonia, lily
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Flower:daffodil##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Flower:balloon-flower##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Flower:daffodil is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Flower:begonia##1
6. Flower:daffodil is somewhere to the left of Flower:balloon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Flower      | begonia  | daffodil | lily        | balloon-flower |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
House: futuristic, modern, victorian, colonial
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and House:victorian##7
2. House:colonial is somewhere to the left of House:futuristic##5
3. House:colonial is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. House:modern is on the left of House:colonial##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| House     | victorian | modern       | colonial         | futuristic     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

