.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
Movie-Genre: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
City: berlin, new-york, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of City:edinburgh##1
2. City:edinburgh is somewhere between City:new-york and City:berlin##7
3. City:san-francisco is on the left of Movie-Genre:scientific##1
4. City:berlin is somewhere between City:edinburgh and Movie-Genre:crime##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| City   | san-francisco | berlin  | edinburgh   | new-york |

