.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
Birthday: september, november, december, april
1. Birthday:april is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Birthday:november and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Birthday:april##1
4. Birthday:december is on the left of Birthday:april##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Birthday:september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Birthday   | november      | september   | december | april  |

