.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
Hobby: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
Pet: goat, dog, snake, pony
1. Pet:pony is on the left or right of Hobby:reading##3
2. Pet:goat is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Hobby:rock-climbing##1
4. Pet:pony is somewhere between Hobby:reading and Hobby:drawing##7
5. Pet:pony is on the left of Pet:snake##1
6. Pet:dog is somewhere to the left of Pet:pony##5
7. Hobby:reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. Hobby:drawing is on the left or right of Hobby:rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| Pet   | goat      | dog | pony      | snake |

