3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
4. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the left of Movie-Genre:romance##1
5. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the left or right of Nationality:nigerian##3
6. Nationality:nigerian is somewhere between Nationality:american and Nationality:dutch##7
7. Nationality:indonesian is somewhere to the right of Movie-Genre:romance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel | zombie      | romance | superhero     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

