2. Job:scientist is on the right of Job:engineer##1
3. Beverage:7up is on the left or right of Job:engineer##3
4. Job:engineer is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
5. Job:scientist is somewhere between Beverage:milk and Job:police-officer##7
6. Beverage:juice is somewhere to the right of Beverage:almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Beverage   | milk         | almond-milk      | 7up | juice            |

